snippet.title: The Lion's Song + The Flower Collectors 🦁 Nintendo Switch trailer 🌸 Super Rare Games
snippet.description:
🌸 Limited physical edition - on sale June 10th, 6pm BST - exclusively at www.superraregames.com 🦁

Includes all episodes of 'The Lion's Song' and 'The Flower Collectors' on on cartridge with a reversible cover; rare print of 4,000 units
